    About Me

    Your Favorite Local Spot!

    New in the local area and looking to have a night out with a few friends? In need of a place that serves quality drinks and great entertainment? Or do you just need a place to kick back after a long day from work? Whatever you need, Copper Kettle Bar & Restaurant is the best place for you. At our pub, you will not only get great drinks but also a great environment. Contact us today for inquires or reservations.

    Food, drink, and entertainment

    Our goal is to ensure our guests are well entertained and well served with only the best foods and drinks. In addition to the full bar, we also provide a variety of home made foods you can choose from, like soups, pastas and burgers. We understand that everyone has their preference and taste, therefore, we take into account every suggestion and provide our guests with gluten free, vegetarian and vegan options. Enjoy these perks while watching your favorite sporting events on one of our five big screen TVs!

    Our Outstanding Staff

    Leave it to our staff to make you feel right at home. Bring Irish owned and operated, we take pride in our team of staff consisting of people from all over the world! If you enjoy a family atmosphere and like a bit of the "craic", you can also join the band of our wide range of satisfied customers who keep coming back. Contact us today or just stop at our pub for a pint!
